snippet.title: Palworld - Official Sakurajima Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Get a look at all the new pals, features, and more on the way in the Palworld Sakurajima Update. The update introduces Xbox dedicated servers, a new building and level cap, new subspecies, a new raid, faction, boss, and more.

The Palworld Sakurajima Update will be released on June 27, 2024 for PC, Xbox Series X/S, and Xbox One.

#IGN #Gaming #Palworld
